&h=ddd4ac0a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90M7Cew.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90M7Cew.png&h=40abe25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBp5oUx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBp5oUx.png&h=7917b9f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1PMSNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1PMSNN.png&h=d9ef5a4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3311a296a792b1140e504c2b996ca12384f8a25","tid":1215022,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"奉勸各位<br />\n唔好做任何犯法嘢 !<br />\n唔好挑釁警方同站長<br />\n我哋只係每朝迫地鐵番工嘅打工仔"},{"pid":"f8176154e0d66c86079af5900b3bdb5a81b8f85b","tid":1215022,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"如果可以<br />\n請以3-5 人一組最好<br />\n一齊企響車門邊<br />\n(咁就算附近有咩阿叔阿伯撩交打, 都唔駛怕佢)<br />\n<br />\n如果有長遮一類工具更好<br />\n唔駛次次出腳"},{"pid":"19f3c4399204c379acec216691f7e9c38dc8981e","tid":1215022,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"記住, 千祈唔好硬碰<br />\n一畀人拉走咗, 就少咗一份力量<br />\n如果畀人一警戒, 就落車去下一班<br />\n反正港鐵咁多班車, 實有一班啱你搭"},{"pid":"bc79fbfca2660316a19bc803a109a45a245d420e","tid":1215022,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"大家要多D休息 千其唔好係地鐵車廂暈低訓係到<br />\n到時就塞地鐵 影響到人就唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n100個連登人 每一個一入車就暈 咁就大獲啦"},{"pid":"638a52bcad5e33f15eed583e2876880e904e9812","tid":1215022,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19f3c4399204c379acec216691f7e9c38dc8981e","tid":1215022,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"記住, 千祈唔好硬碰<br />\n一畀人拉走咗, 就少咗一份力量<br />\n如果畀人一警戒, 就落車去下一班<br />\n反正港鐵咁多班車, 實有一班啱你搭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06